<HEADLINE>
<P>
RETURN TO THE BOOTH BY REAGAN PRODUCES DIVIDED CONSTITUENCY 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Vin Scully must have been terribly embarrassed with his novice color man by the 
end of the first inning. I thought it would never end. If he got paid more than 
a free hot dog, it would be too much. 
</P>
<P>
I hope in the future Scully's protege will stick to horseback riding, where he 
has a lot more experience. 
</P>
<P>
JAMES HARRINGTON 
</P>
<P>
Glendale 
</P>
</TEXT>
