<HEADLINE>
<P>
DOUG COLLINS DESERVED BETTER FROM THE BULLS 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Does anyone really understand the firing of Doug Collins as coach of the 
Chicago Bulls? 
</P>
<P>
Here's a man who helped his organization make quantum leaps toward credibility 
and respectability in recent years and come within a heartbeat of the NBA 
finals this year. 
</P>
<P>
But instead of a much-deserved pat on the back and a contract extension, they 
gave him the air. Collins deserved better. 
</P>
<P>
ROSS PATTERSON 
</P>
<P>
Burbank 
</P>
