<P>
AMERICAN LEGION BASEBALL; 
</P>
<P>
LJUBETIC'S FOURTH HIT LIFTS VAN NUYS TO 8-7 VICTORY 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Tony Ljubetic had four hits, including a game-winning single in the eighth 
inning, to lift Van Nuys-Notre Dame to an 8-7 victory over Sun Valley in an 
Eastern Division District 20 American Legion baseball game Friday at Poly High. 
</P>
<P>
Van Nuys-Notre Dame (10-10) parlayed five hits into six runs in the third and 
scored again in the fourth. Kevin Milligan had three hits and four teammates 
had two each. 
</P>
<P>
