all-male roster in 1987. GARY FRIEDMAN / Los Angeles Times; Photo, Paulette 
Attie ; Photo, Bohemian Club in San Francisco continues to turn away women. 
ANNE DOWIE; Photo, Municipal Judge Lois Anderson Smaltz says she was royally 
welcomed as a member of the Jonathan Club in 1987. The club's facilities occupy 
a beachfront site in Santa Monica. SARAH M. BROWN; GEORGE FRY / Los Angeles 
Times; Photo, Jan Bradshaw Los Angeles Times 
</P>
