</P>
<P>
Material Handler: Unknown 
</P>
<P>
Materials Involved: Diesel fuel 
</P>
<P>
</P>
<P>
Date: May 9 
</P>
<P>
Location of Incident: Valle Road at southbound Interstate 5, San Juan 
Capistrano 
</P>
<P>
Material Handler: Unknown-illegal disposal 
</P>
<P>
Materials Involved: Waste thinner 
</P>
<P>
</P>
<P>
Date: May 11 
</P>
<P>
Location of Incident: Crown Valley Parkway &amp; Forbes Road, Laguna Hills 
</P>
<P>
Material Handler: Dal Chem Inc. 
</P>
