<HEADLINE>
<P>
BIBLE DRIVE STARTS 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
By AP 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<DATELINE>
<P>
NEW YORK 
</P>
</DATELINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
The Baptist World Alliance presented a $100,000 check to the American Bible 
Society at its annual meeting to help open a drive to provide a million Bibles 
and New Testaments to people of the Soviet Union and Eastern Europe. 
</P>
