All-Star games and not one of them has played? 
</P>
<P>
38) Has anyone noticed that Angel left-handers have a 21-11 record this year, 
as opposed to 11-16 in 1988? 
</P>
<P>
39) Can you believe that Abbott has a better record than Witt? 
</P>
<P>
40) Why did the Brewers trade Bill Schroeder? 
</P>
<P>
41) If Devon White's batting average continues to slide, will the same thing 
happen to his place in the order? 
</P>
<P>
42) Will Jim Eppard ever get to stay in Anaheim long enough to establish a 
mailing address? 
</P>
<P>
43) Will someone remind me not to let the Angels' Quad Cities affiliate book my 
hotel reservations? 
</P>
<P>
44) Who has bigger arms, Brian Downing or Bo? 
</P>
<P>
45) Is it possible to reduce the size of the Angel halo on the caps? It looks 
like a doughnut. 
</P>
<P>
46) Why is it no one is talking about the Kansas City Royals? 
</P>
<P>
47) Can it be true: The Angels don't miss Bob Boone? 
</P>
<P>
48) Do you think Gene Mauch regrets his decision not to return as Angel 
manager? 
</P>
<P>
49) You know those miniature toy figures of major league baseball players that 
are the rage? Is it true the Jose Canseco model shows him signing a speeding 
ticket? 
</P>
<P>
50) Did Ronald Reagan really say that Anaheim Stadium was the most beautiful 
ballpark in America? 
</P>
<P>
51) Do you think Reagan might have forever cost his party the Republican 
precincts in the Fenway Park and Wrigley Field area? 
</P>
