LUCERO WINS FEATURE AT SPEEDWAY EVENT 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Steve Lucero of Riverside won the four-lap main event in the weekly speedway 
program at the Orange County Fairgrounds Friday in Costa Mesa. 
</P>
<P>
